OL,3,CBridgwater Carnival calls for more
OL,4,Csupport in the face of rising costs
OL,6,FThe organisers of one of Somerset's
OL,7,Foldest and biggest carnivals are
OL,8,Fcalling on the government for help
OL,9,Fwith rising costs.
OL,11,FThe Bridgwater Carnival Committee and
OL,12,Flocal MP Ashley Fox have met with
OL,13,FCulture Minister Stephanie Peacock to
OL,14,Fdiscuss the strain of putting on such
OL,15,Flarge events.
OL,17,FBridgwater Carnival President Dave
OL,18,FCreedy told ITV West Country the event
OL,19,Fneeded to be "future-proofed".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
