PN,43702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1776355854
OL,3,CBridgwater Carnival calls for more
OL,4,Csupport in the face of rising costs
OL,6,FHe explained: "The costs are greater
OL,7,Fnow than they've ever been. There is
OL,8,Falways extra red tape involved and
OL,9,Fthings we need to keep on top of.
OL,11,F"The minister was very responsive, to
OL,12,Fbe fair."
OL,14,FMr Creedy added: "We could do with
OL,15,Fmore support from the general public
OL,16,Fwho come along, it's a free event, but
OL,17,Fwe do have costs."
OL,19,FHe noted that collections on the night
OL,20,Fend up being less because less people
OL,21,Fcarry cash.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
