PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1776355854
OL,3,CBridgwater Carnival calls for more
OL,4,Csupport in the face of rising costs
OL,6,FA government spokesperson said: "We're
OL,7,Fcommitted to supporting the sector
OL,8,Fthrough the upcoming Visitor Economy
OL,9,FGrowth Strategy that will set out a
OL,10,Flong-term plan to increase visitor
OL,11,Fflows across the UK, boost value and
OL,12,Fdeliver sustainable growth.
OL,14,F"The UK also has one of the world's
OL,15,Fmost generous tax regimes for the
OL,16,Fsector, providing over #7 billion in
OL,17,Fsupport last year alone, including
OL,18,Fexemptions from paying business rates,
OL,19,Fa range of VAT reliefs and the long
OL,20,Frunning Gift Aid scheme."
